{"tid":1090780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因製「銘記八酒六四」酒，被控尋釁滋事罪，判監三年","createTime":"2019-04-03T16:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T18:35:52.000Z","uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a75a65fd40406ea8c543f3ebce923e113a5ce874","tid":1090780,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"【六四酒案次被告張雋永罪成 判三緩四】<br />\n<br />\n六四酒案周二在四川成都中級法院繼續審理，次被告張雋永尋釁滋事罪罪成，判監三年、緩刑四年，即日獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n張雋永三年前與另外三人，因自製一款叫「銘記八酒六四」的酒而被捕。首被告符海陸周一被判監三年、緩刑五年。<br />\n<br />\n#六四酒案<br />\n#張雋永<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2080367048774437?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2080367048774437%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5LtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=a85897a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2080367048774437?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"f136248d1829587e328d32937a2a53f1245dc254","tid":1090780,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2017/06/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8-20170604174105_94ba_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2017%2F06%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%25A4%25A8-20170604174105_94ba_large.jpg&h=da91cb22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3930ce26c5fc75427f313de17656150074639bff","tid":1090780,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"要攪你的話，實會攪出個原因"},{"pid":"8083cdf99f1fb31a3d1ee67439da9e9d04b96d55","tid":1090780,"uid":64374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26f07be2049fb0fffa918ef9739f15138612fc6f","tid":1090780,"uid":58503,"like"